{"words":[{"word":"place","count":4},{"word":"give","count":3},{"word":"going","count":3},{"word":"td","count":3},{"word":"wonder","count":2},{"word":"sigh","count":2},{"word":"data","count":2},{"word":"problem","count":2},{"word":"shift","count":2},{"word":"useless","count":2},{"word":"try","count":2},{"word":"induction","count":2},{"word":"cell","count":2},{"word":"mean","count":2},{"word":"tds","count":2},{"word":"anything","count":2},{"word":"done","count":2},{"word":"act","count":2},{"word":"thinking","count":2},{"word":"person","count":2},{"word":"tried","count":2},{"word":"indeed","count":1},{"word":"roof","count":1},{"word":"punctured","count":1},{"word":"cleanly","count":1},{"word":"large","count":1},{"word":"rock","count":1},{"word":"repair","count":1},{"word":"everything's","count":1},{"word":"breaking","count":1},{"word":"lately","count":1},{"word":"incursion","count":1},{"word":"records","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"restoring","count":1},{"word":"needed","count":1},{"word":"either","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"properly","count":1},{"word":"nearby","count":1},{"word":"exiles","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"steal","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"usually","count":1},{"word":"food","count":1},{"word":"scrap","count":1},{"word":"metals","count":1},{"word":"stuff","count":1},{"word":"guts","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"keeping","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"yammering","count":1},{"word":"physical","count":1},{"word":"reminder","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"movement","count":1},{"word":"outside","count":1},{"word":"tsk","count":1},{"word":"guys","count":1},{"word":"business","count":1},{"word":"outnumbered","count":1},{"word":"gonna","count":1},{"word":"skills","count":1},{"word":"guard","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"anywhere","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"goes","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"letting","count":1},{"word":"turning","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1},{"word":"covering","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"taken","count":1},{"word":"care","count":1},{"word":"check","count":1},{"word":"transfer","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"almost","count":1},{"word":"complete","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"radar","count":1},{"word":"station","count":1},{"word":"ever","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"battle","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"sense","count":1},{"word":"airheads","count":1},{"word":"dead","count":1},{"word":"end","count":1},{"word":"good-old","count":1},{"word":"beating","count":1},{"word":"deal","count":1},{"word":"clowns","count":1},{"word":"expect","count":1},{"word":"luck","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"digginig","count":1},{"word":"garbage","count":1},{"word":"dump","count":1},{"word":"ziqin","count":1},{"word":"zhiyou","count":1},{"word":"nianhan","count":1},{"word":"nine","count":1},{"word":"rangers","count":1},{"word":"stationed","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"knowing","count":1},{"word":"escaping","count":1},{"word":"collected","count":1},{"word":"frequency","count":1},{"word":"evolution","count":1},{"word":"rate","count":1},{"word":"spot","count":1},{"word":"using","count":1},{"word":"quirk","count":1},{"word":"copying","count":1},{"word":"human","count":1},{"word":"behaviors","count":1},{"word":"guided","count":1},{"word":"destroy","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"heap","count":1},{"word":"experience","count":1},{"word":"research","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"checks","count":1},{"word":"box","count":1},{"word":"realize","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"tough","count":1},{"word":"kept","count":1},{"word":"mumbling","count":1},{"word":"pain","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"complain","count":1},{"word":"continued","count":1},{"word":"moving","count":1},{"word":"learned","count":1},{"word":"tactics","count":1},{"word":"whenever","count":1},{"word":"defended","count":1},{"word":"surveillance","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"seized","count":1},{"word":"guarded","count":1},{"word":"capture","count":1},{"word":"protected","count":1},{"word":"researcher","count":1},{"word":"rushed","count":1},{"word":"means","count":1},{"word":"resist","count":1},{"word":"faster","count":1},{"word":"adapt","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Indeed. The roof has been punctured cleanly through by a large rock.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"I wonder if we can repair it... *sigh*... Everything's breaking down all over the place lately...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Incursion records? I thought restoring the data was all we needed to do?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"*sigh* It's either one problem or the other. I can't even hand over my shift properly. How useless I am...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Come to think of it... Nearby Exiles sometimes come here to steal things.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"But they usually go for food or scrap metals, stuff like that. They don’t have the guts to try and take something like this... What happened this time?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Out with it. Where are you keeping the Induction Cell?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Enough yammering. Just tell us where it is!","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"How about a physical reminder on the head. Eh?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Fine. We’ll find it ourselves.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Wait... I hear movement outside!","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Tsk... These guys look like they mean business...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"They’ve got us outnumbered, what are we gonna do...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"You’ve got some skills I’ll give you that, but don’t get your guard down...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Yeah, these TDs aren’t going anywhere anyway... Here goes nothing. I’m not letting anything get in my way of turning in this shift!","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Good thing I had {PlayerName} covering my back... Wouldn’t have done it without {Male=him;Female=her}...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"So... Now that we’ve taken care of our TD problem. How about we check on the data transfer?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"If it's already done, then my work here is almost complete...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"...Don't give up. There's still a place we haven't been to yet.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"The radar station. We should give the place a look.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"The place’s been like this ever since that battle...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"It’s just an act. I’ve seen it all before.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"You try talk sense to these airheads and all you’re going to get is a dead end.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Some good-old beating is the only way to deal with these clowns.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Didn’t expect my luck to make a turn from digginig through a garbage dump...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Tell me you're not thinking what I think you're thinking...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"…","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"…","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"…","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Ziqin, Zhiyou, Nianhan... It’s the nine Rangers that were stationed here together with me.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"You mean to tell me that this person, knowing he’s got no way of escaping, collected the frequency of the TD’s evolution rate on the spot, and by using their quirk of of copying human behaviors, guided it to destroy itself?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"To do this, you have to be someone with a heap of experience in TD research.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"As far as I know, there’s only one person that checks the box ...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"...I didn’t realize you went through all of this... I even tried to act tough on you, and kept mumbling on and on...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"You're in as much pain as I am... but you didn't stop or complain, and continued moving on...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"I'm just... so useless. No wonder I can't do anything right...","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"…","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"...You're right.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"That's how they learned our tactics! Whenever we defended a surveillance point, they seized it. When we guarded an Induction Cell, they tried to capture it. And when we protected the researcher, the TDs rushed for him too.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Which means that the more we resist, the faster they adapt? What are we going to do about it?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004}]}